<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0182a" xml:id="I01.0072.0182a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0182a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 72</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0182a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>彭城王高浟修寺碑</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0182a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0182a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0182a0101">造碑人比
<lb ed="I" n="0182a02" type="honorific"/>丘僧弁選
<lb ed="I" n="0182a03" type="honorific"/>年九十四
<lb ed="I" n="0182a04" type="honorific"/>　　讚三
<lb ed="I" n="0182a05" type="honorific"/>　　寶福
<lb ed="I" n="0182a06" type="honorific"/>　　業碑
<lb ed="I" n="0182a07" type="honorific"/>齊太師錄
<lb ed="I" n="0182a08" type="honorific"/>尚書事彭
<lb ed="I" n="0182a09" type="honorific"/>城王高浟</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0182b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0182b0101">聞夫開士弘教。至人崇道。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">嗟</unclear>三界之危苦。悼□生之□□。將欲□□□□。□□舟樑。勢位同於
<lb ed="I" n="0182b02" type="honorific"/>脫屣。國城均於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">棄</unclear>唾。然則勇猛不息。非為獨善。感通<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">所</unclear>□。利□塵沙。是故大覺乘時。慈悲一切。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b03" type="honorific"/>持智炬於昏境。擊法鼓於<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182001" n="0182001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182001" n="0182001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182001" n="0182001"/>聾<anchor xml:id="end0182001"/>俗。迷<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182002" n="0182002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182002" n="0182002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182002" n="0182002"/>邪<anchor xml:id="end0182002"/>反正。黑暗<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">遷</unclear>明。應物有期。世雄示滅。運神功於忍土。布靈
<lb ed="I" n="0182b04" type="honorific"/>迹於大千。雙樹嵐鞞之下。乃興妙塔。顯節涼臺之上。驗諸圖象。思崇真正。世有人焉。冥中見曉。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b05" type="honorific"/>復鍾□覺。太師錄尚書事彭城王。峰峻鍾山。枝華寶樹。心薀天璞。器孕<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182003" n="0182003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182003" n="0182003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182003" n="0182003"/>全<anchor xml:id="end0182003"/>才。懸明鏡以臨方。置
<lb ed="I" n="0182b06" type="honorific"/>歸墟而受物。多藝遺姬旦之能。樹德蔑劉蒼之善。天之所縱。不獨人中。化金練石之方。時為陋
<lb ed="I" n="0182b07" type="honorific"/>術外生。調微之義。仍謂蕨言。窮神逐變。探冥弘道。藻身法海。竦慮玄門。以皮肉為坏器。以性<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">命</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0182b08" type="honorific"/>為畫水。得寶藏於身<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">中</unclear>。識金珠於額上。曰者□<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182004" n="0182004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182004" n="0182004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182004" n="0182004"/>驂<anchor xml:id="end0182004"/>北邁。作牧維城。屈跡行春風之恩。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182005" n="0182005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182005" n="0182005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182005" n="0182005"/>局<anchor xml:id="end0182005"/>道為<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">秋</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0182b09" type="honorific"/>駕之術。循□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">問</unclear>邑。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">褰</unclear>襜高<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">視</unclear>。爰有勝地。宿置伽藍。南望呼沱。漢騎蹈冰之所。北臨易水。燕臣<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">行</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0182b10" type="honorific"/>歌之蹤。界<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear>俠藪。躡野縈林。泄雲<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">濆</unclear>雨。□珠□□。以茲博敞。寔栖靈聖。於是輟駕委心。慇懃至
<lb ed="I" n="0182b11" type="honorific"/>道。悵房廡之隳壞。恨欹闕之不工。爰慕五<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>。放□□之法。乃懷三<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">劉</unclear>。興鏤金之想。徘徊正念。意
<lb ed="I" n="0182b12" type="honorific"/>在於斯。及謁帝文□。入牽人寶。星<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">火</unclear>數迴。攝心彌篤。□□家臣。逾存經紀。搜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">素</unclear>珉青碧之珍。伐
<lb ed="I" n="0182b13" type="honorific"/>貞松<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">文</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">梓</unclear>之木。揆星<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">成</unclear>則。測日為准。架室□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">雙</unclear>林之下。構<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">尊</unclear>像毗舍之地。龍王愧巧。天帝<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182006" n="0182006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182006" n="0182006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182006" n="0182006"/>慚<anchor xml:id="end0182006"/>工。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b14" type="honorific"/>懸如意於暗中。不勞燈炬。置炎光於鍑下。自然香食。至如琢龍次<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">玉</unclear>。摹立靈象。妙範合聖。奇相
<lb ed="I" n="0182b15" type="honorific"/>通神。光絕金膏。明兼銀燭。成就等應見之容。圓滿<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">若</unclear>下生之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">狀</unclear>。□僧德眾。踵至如林。憑心正路。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b16" type="honorific"/>絕迹疑<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182007" n="0182007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182007" n="0182007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182007" n="0182007"/>網<anchor xml:id="end0182007"/>。持法鉤以牽毒。流智水以銷煩。戒行周圓。衿神空淨。圍繞晝夜。讚嘆頂禮。香氣如臺。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b17" type="honorific"/>花浮成蓋。風林搖薄。生微妙之音。蓮<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182008" n="0182008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182008" n="0182008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182008" n="0182008"/>沼<anchor xml:id="end0182008"/>環迴。發哀雅之韻。翻同天上駕御之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182009" n="0182009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182009" n="0182009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182009" n="0182009"/>園<anchor xml:id="end0182009"/>。鬱似人間花林
<lb ed="I" n="0182b18" type="honorific"/>之窟。資父事君。奉<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">國</unclear>遺己。宣茲願力。上奉　皇家世祀。共圓□周。久隆基興。方地齊固。乘寶殿
<lb ed="I" n="0182b19" type="honorific"/>以飛空。駕金輪而傍轉。珠囊不委。玉鏡恒暉。蠢蠢□生。咸歸□覺。若夫一念小善。猶居忉利之
<lb ed="I" n="0182b20" type="honorific"/>上。兩錢輕拖。仍成羅漢之果。況乃據<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0182b2001" n="0182b2001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182b2001" n="0182b2001"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0182b2001"/>憂之土。立大乘之宅。業深金剛之海。功□□玉之山。歸
<lb ed="I" n="0182b21" type="honorific"/>生生之福。出死死之苦。永銷煩惚。畢竟清涼。勒茲琬琰。弘此偈讚。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b22" type="honorific"/>迷路遙緬。欲境<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182010" n="0182010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182010" n="0182010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182010" n="0182010"/>遼<anchor xml:id="end0182010"/>闊。輪轉無窮。環循不脫。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">性</unclear>猶狂<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182011" n="0182011"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182011" n="0182011"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182011" n="0182011"/>象<anchor xml:id="end0182011"/>。命同聚沫。毒箭傍侵。風刀下割。無名至道。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b23" type="honorific"/>權應時來。一音所說。万路咸開。人天迴向。魔梵俱摧。永懷寂滅。言昇妙臺。棺踊金色。林成鵠變。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b24" type="honorific"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182012" n="0182012"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182012" n="0182012"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182012" n="0182012"/>寶<anchor xml:id="end0182012"/>聚常湛。三乘東轉。喆人合道。英猷獨扇。乃隆磬石。　皇心逾睠。時應刺舉。南面維蕃。相彼□
<lb ed="I" n="0182b25" type="honorific"/>地。竦意祗<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>園<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>。雕<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182013" n="0182013"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182013" n="0182013"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182013" n="0182013"/>墻<anchor xml:id="end0182013"/>通閣。繡柱朱門。高堂夏冷。幽室冬溫。爰圖色象。瑩磨成質。形類金山。項猶<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">朝</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0182b26" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">日</unclear>。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182014" n="0182014"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182014" n="0182014"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182014" n="0182014"/>思<anchor xml:id="end0182014"/>極神造。妙窮化術。真謂飛來。全同涌出。珊瑚為蓋。琉璃作<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>網<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>。寶鑷搖音。靈鍾震響。樹名□
<lb ed="I" n="0182b27" type="honorific"/>脫。花稱<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0182b2701" n="0182b2701"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182b2701" n="0182b2701"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0182b2701"/>想。或鄣長袪。法門遂廣。磬此誓願。　皇道重明。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear>鼓恒韻。神鼎不輕。官府万國。朝□
<lb ed="I" n="0182b28" type="honorific"/>□靈。勒茲不朽。蘭菊其馨。　大齊太寧二年歲次壬午二月辛丑朔八日戊申。造訖故記之。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b29" type="honorific"/>僕射魏收造文　元建造寺主齊輔□兒侄等　碑主安<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0182015" n="0182015"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0182015" n="0182015"/><anchor xml:id="beg0182015" n="0182015"/>喜<anchor xml:id="end0182015"/>堤<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">陽</unclear>人小字劉永長名<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">選</unclear></p>
